    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/f15a6bc09bf46c3a3fbb41df894d7bd9.avif?t=1768248874\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras_big/f15a6bc09bf46c3a3fbb41df894d7bd9.avif?t=1768248874 width=800 height=195 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>一项机密实验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEPRISION是一款第一人称生存恐怖游戏，专注于在一个机密的心理操控实验中的心理生存。被困在强制意识状态中，你的思维成为前进和坚持下去的唯一方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/31f51ef20b0b1cf8c84d38f6dc62570f.poster.avif?t=1768248874\" width=800 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/31f51ef20b0b1cf8c84d38f6dc62570f.webm?t=1768248874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/31f51ef20b0b1cf8c84d38f6dc62570f.mp4?t=1768248874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>扭曲的记忆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索由个人记忆与经历构建、如今被改变与扭曲的环境。熟悉的地点逐渐化为充满敌意的空间，你必须小心前行，留意周围环境以及潜伏其中的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/3d11fcc09191796266de75fa0dbd63ee.poster.avif?t=1768248874\" width=800 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/3d11fcc09191796266de75fa0dbd63ee.webm?t=1768248874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/3d11fcc09191796266de75fa0dbd63ee.mp4?t=1768248874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>个人威胁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你所面对的威胁既非陌生，也非冷漠无关。它们是与你过去深度相连的具象化存在，被设计用来引发情绪痛苦与持续紧张。你的生存将取决于你探索环境、管理有限资源、规避危险以及在压力下做出决定的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/ca12f029c7a2a346320e1fef61e5b4f6.poster.avif?t=1768248874\" width=800 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/ca12f029c7a2a346320e1fef61e5b4f6.webm?t=1768248874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804730/extras/ca12f029c7a2a346320e1fef61e5b4f6.mp4?t=1768248874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>心理生存恐怖</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《DEPRISION》专注于压迫感十足、以叙事驱动的心理恐怖体验，在这里，氛围、声音以及不确定性与眼前所见同样重要。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "西班牙语 - 西班牙, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 简体中文, 韩语, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 意大利语, 加泰罗尼亚语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
